<template>
  <v-dialog v-model="show" persistent max-width="290" >
    <v-card>
      <v-card-title class="text-h5 primary">
        Warning
      </v-card-title>

      <v-card-text>
        憑證金額不夠，請申請憑證
      </v-card-text>

      <v-divider></v-divider>

      <v-card-actions>
        <v-spacer></v-spacer>
        <v-btn color="primary" text @click.stop="show=false"> 知道了 </v-btn>
      </v-card-actions>
    </v-card>
  </v-dialog>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  props: {
     value: Boolean
  },
  computed: {
    show: {
      get () {
        return this.value
      },
      set (value) {
         this.$emit('input', value)
      }
    }
  }
};
</script>

<style>
</style>
